long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bug Bebop is a delightful Google Chrome extension that transforms the way you debug code. Say goodbye to the monotony of compilation errors with Bug Bebop's playful sound effects. As you code on LeetCode, Bug Bebop adds a touch of humor and entertainment to the debugging process, making it a fun and engaging experience. Whether you're a seasoned developer or just starting your coding journey, Bug Bebop is here to inject some joy into your coding sessions.
